Podcast: Partnering with the Frenemy
Google and Samsung. Nike and Foot Locker. Mobileye and Tesla. Business partnerships are critical, yet 50-60% fail. Professor Sandy Jap discusses frenemies in business, common pitfalls of partnering, and preserving alliances in a competitive environment.
